æFrom Phil to Alina, my wife and love of my life.
For memories of lunches and moments shared
in Berkeley Square Mayfair and in
the London Town that we grew to love together
and call our home."»
≈[LEFT]
Angel
Occasionally, we are graced with the presence of an
earth bound angel. They are unable to stay with us for
long, but while they do, they bring unexpected joy
and happiness to all they touch.

[RIGHT]
Eva
07-10-2001  ~ 07-12-2003
Chasing pigeons, feeding ducks, in spite of illness 
living every moment" 
